en.name: 6B45 armored rig (General Purpose)
en.description: A full plate carrier setup built on the 6B45 vest. This setup gives the user a compact yet versatile space for carrying essential gear.

en.name: Ferro Concepts FCPC V5 Plate Carrier (Black Division)
en.description: The fifth-generation FCPC plate carrier continues Ferro Conceptsâ€™ focus on lightweight, adaptable gear. In this version, the plate bags and carrier contour have been redesigned for improved comfort and mobility. Coyote Brown version. Equipped with two radios for communicating with both the assigned squad and HQ.

en.name: WARTECH MK3 TV-104 chest rig (Moss)
en.description: This chest rig platform is designed for placing equipment in the chest and abdomen areas, with an open back. Includes integrated pouches, designed for 8 magazines. Can be used both separately and on top of the armor vest. Manufactured by WARTECH. Moss camouflage version.

en.name: First Spear Siege-R Optimized M.A.S.S. Plate Carrier (Black Division)
en.description: A Siege-R Optimized plate carrier equipped with the M.A.S.S. Shoulder System. Provides reliable all-around protection while offering ample workspace for equipment placement. Black version.

en.name: Spiritus Systems LV-119 Plate Carrier (Black Division V2)
en.description: A highly customizable modular plate carrier by Spiritus Systems, built for maximum comfort in combat. Black version. This setup is equipped with breaching charges and multiple GP pouches for maximum equipment flexibility.

en.description: An improved lightweight version of the standard plate carrier manufactured by Stich Profi. MARPAT Woodland camouflage version.

en.name: ANA Tactical Alpha chest rig (A-TACS AU)
en.description: "Alpha" is a high-quality chest rig that fully meets the military standards for reliability and functionality. The combination of integrated pouches and MOLLE straps provides the means of carrying a large number of necessary equipment. The vest is designed as a classic chest rig. In this type of vest, all the gear is located in the front and side parts, while the back part is comprised of adjustment belts and straps. Manufactured by ANA Tactical. A-TACS AU camouflage version.
